WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:02.559
For fields with a predefined set of values,

1
00:00:02.569 --> 00:00:04.469
such as a task's State field,

2
00:00:04.690 --> 00:00:07.570
the column menu displays a list of available options.

3
00:00:08.699 --> 00:00:11.010
Select one or more values to filter the list.

4
00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:13.039
Then click Apply.

5
00:00:13.810 --> 00:00:16.340
The applied condition appears in the Filter Panel

6
00:00:16.579 --> 00:00:18.739
where it can be reviewed or adjusted.

7
00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:22.899
For free text fields such as a task's Short Description,

8
00:00:23.319 --> 00:00:26.280
the column menu allows you to search for matching text.

9
00:00:26.559 --> 00:00:28.100
Choose the appropriate operator,

10
00:00:28.450 --> 00:00:30.909
such as Starts With or Contains.

11
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.290
Enter the word or phrase you're looking for,

12
00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:34.720
then click Apply.

13
00:00:36.419 --> 00:00:37.740
As with other filters,

14
00:00:37.909 --> 00:00:40.209
the condition is added to the Filter Panel.
